#https://ualinux.com/ru/stream/ispolzovanie-sinkhronizatsii-s-google-drive-v-unity-xfce-i-drugikh-okruzheniyakh-rabochego-stola
#https://ubuntu-mate.community/t/google-drive-and-onedrive-integration/12815/2
